h was published in the journal *Nature*, found that the new drug was effective in treating a range of diseases; the researchers also noted that the drug had a low rate of side effects.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"This choice does not follow from the information given or contains a calculation error. Choice D is incorrect because it either misreads the passage, overgeneralizes a limited detail, or focuses on information irrelevant to the question stem. Re-read the sentences surrounding the key detail before eliminating this option on test day."}]'::jsonb,
